data.description: 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom 2 cars garage in the exclusive enclave of Windward Isle at River Bridge. Master bedroom features dual sinks, soaking tub, with walking closet. Outdoors, you will enjoy a lovely backyard with pool. It is near to the Turnpike, I-95, Wellington, Boynton Beach, Downtown West Palm Beach, stunning local beaches,PBI international airport. Community is a well-kept gated neighborhood that provides its residents with a number of resort-style amenities
